high_descs: Turn left and go to the sofa.
Pick up the tomato closer to the front of the sofa.
Turn around and go across to the microwave.
Place the tomato in the microwave and heat the tomato, then pick it up.
Turn around and go to the dining table.
Place the tomato on the dining table in the right corner,in front of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated tomato on the dining table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the sofa
Pick the tomato from the sofa.
Turn left and walk towards the microwave .
Put the tomato inside the microwave and pick it back after few seconds.
Head around and walk towards the dining table.
Place the tomato on the table.
anns.task_desc: To place the tomato on the table.

high_descs: Head rotate and turn left to the sofa.
Pick the tomato from the sofa.
Head rotate and walk towards the microwave.
Place the tomato inside the microwave.
Pick it back and turn left to the dining table.
Place the tomato on the table.
anns.task_desc: To place the tomato on the table.
